"{\"uid\": \"thestar.com.my-news-world-2024-07-29-olympics--china039s-equestrian-rider-alex-hua-tian-facing-setback-in-eventing\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Monday, 29 Jul 2024  VERSAILLES, France, July 28 (Xinhua) -- Chinese equestrian rider Alex Hua Tian encountered a setback in the cross-country phase of the eventing competition at the Paris Olympics on Sunday, resulting in a penalty of 20.6 points.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.13956939991124e-16, \"text\": \"Xinhua\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 61, \"end\": 68, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8168658268020771, \"rank\": 0.22251904346733561, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 86, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Hua_Tian\", \"score\": 0.9999999999558895, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Hua Tian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Hua_Tian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Hua_Tian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Combined with his dressage penalties on Saturday, Hua Tian's total penalty score amounted to 42.6 points, causing his ranking to plummet from 3rd to 32nd.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"score\": 0.9972705443061053, \"rank\": 0.002736925979209247, \"text\": \"Tian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event took place under clear skies at the historic Palace of Versailles, drawing a large crowd, while the cross-country phase saw several incidents, including falls from competitors from Germany, Ecuador and Portugal, leading to their elimination.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9429022614980165, \"rank\": 0.035151985125100184, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9985790815829503, \"rank\": 0.001386302092410135, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hua Tian faced a controversial penalty during his run.\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"score\": 0.9972705443061053, \"rank\": 0.002736925979209247, \"text\": \"Tian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Broadcast footage showed a judge unexpectedly appearing in front of obstacle 21B.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hua Tian and his horse Chocs made a sidestep to the left before jumping right over the obstacle.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"score\": 0.9972705443061053, \"rank\": 0.002736925979209247, \"text\": \"Tian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The horse brushed against a flag on the left side of the obstacle, resulting in a 15-point penalty.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China promptly protested to event organizers, but the International Equestrian Federation has yet to issue an official response.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9994269066070369, \"rank\": 0.0004625942626310662, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jia Dapeng, leader of China's equestrian team, told reporters that the team has \\\"reviewed the footage with the technical representatives and expressed our stance\\\".\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heavenly_Stems\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.141028970427086e-12, \"text\": \"Jia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heavenly_Stems\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Heavenly_Stems\"}, {\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dapeng_Subdistrict\", \"score\": 0.8293473582944879, \"rank\": 0.2056744848246515, \"text\": \"Dapeng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dapeng_Subdistrict\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dapeng_Subdistrict\"}, {\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9994269066070369, \"rank\": 0.0004625942626310662, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9529440218103091, \"rank\": 0.04453659141816196, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that the team, nevertheless, will respect the \\\"rules and results from the federation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hua Tian revealed that his horse took a light step to the left before jumping right.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"score\": 0.9972705443061053, \"rank\": 0.002736925979209247, \"text\": \"Tian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think this happened because, unfortunately, there was one of the jump judges running a little bit on the landing side behind.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think that really distracted Chocs,\\\" Hua Tian said.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1647, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"score\": 0.9972705443061053, \"rank\": 0.002736925979209247, \"text\": \"Tian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tian_Jia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The other Chinese rider, Sun Huadong, withdrew from the competition due to his horse Lady suffering from swelling in her left foreleg.\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.8168658268020771, \"rank\": 0.22251904346733561, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Germany's Michael Jung topped the individual leaderboard with a total of 17.80 penalty points, surpassing Britain's Laura Collett, who incurred 0.8 time penalties in the cross-country phase, finishing with 18.30 penalty points.\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9429022614980165, \"rank\": 0.035151985125100184, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_E._Jung\", \"score\": 0.9988531015031434, \"rank\": 0.0011482035875299884, \"text\": \"Michael Jung\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_E._Jung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_E._Jung\"}, {\"begin\": 1901, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9973153346878421, \"rank\": 0.0022212437683903808, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.o